Here are the most basic and important shortcuts that you should know

alt + enter-Shows fixes to an error
ctrl + c-Copies
ctrl + v-Pastes
ctrl + d-duplicate what line you are on to the next line or duplicates what is highlighted right next to it
ctrl + alt + o-imports anything that needs to be imported
ctrl + alt + l-Formats code
ctrl + alt + shift + t-Brings up refracting menu
ctrl + k-Shows window to commit code
